note: Me llamo Leonardo y tengo 23 años. Soy esposo, padre, trabajador asalariado y estudiante de ingeniería en desarrollo de software. También soy estoico porque mi esposa no me deja ser cínico.

fields.name: Ecclesiastes 4:2-3
fields.value: So I congratulated the dead who are already dead more than the living who are still living. But better off than both of them is the one who has never existed, who has never seen the evil activity that is done under the sun.

fields.name: Shadow of the Season-Screaming Trees 1:11
fields.value: Said, "Lord please give me what I need" He said, "There's pain and misery"
